data.description: If your looking for a lake get-a-way close to the lake and boat ramps here's the one. Located in Cardinal Cove just two blocks from boat ramps and fishing piers. Fenced, 2 car carport, small storage building, front and back decks. Roof was installed 4 months ago, septic is 7 years old, hot water tank 2 yrs old and outside freshly painted.  Large master bedroom with split bedroom lay out, open concept living room, eating area and kitchen. Well maintained and ready for new owners.  Sellers will need to stay till end of the year.
